; ********************************************************
; * Drive checks and assigns                             *
; ********************************************************

Infoq >T:Drives VOLUMES

; Clear Tools Daemon Menu File

Delete >NIL: S:ToolsDaemon.menu

; Copy a blank Tools Daemon file from S:

Copy S:ToolsDaemonMenus/ToolsDaemon.Blank S:ToolsDaemon.menu

If $PiStorm EQ "1"
Assign SHARED: PCO:Shared
EndIf

; ************************************************************************************************
; * AGS requires Workbench, Work, AGS_Drive and at least one of the WHDLoad drives as a minimum. *
; * All other drives are optional and the following scripts will add any menus as required.      *
; ************************************************************************************************

; Append the main required menus to the blank file.

Append S:ToolsDaemonMenus/Toolsdaemon.Main S:ToolsDaemon.menu 

Search >NIL: T:Drives Music QUIET
If not warn
 Execute S:Music-Stuff
 Append S:ToolsDaemonMenus/Toolsdaemon.Music S:ToolsDaemon.menu
Endif

Search >NIL: T:Drives Emulators1 QUIET
If not warn
 Assign Emulators: Emulators1:
 Append S:ToolsDaemonMenus/Toolsdaemon.Emulators S:ToolsDaemon.menu
Endif

Search >NIL: T:Drives Emulators2 QUIET
If not warn
 Append S:ToolsDaemonMenus/Toolsdaemon.Scummvm S:ToolsDaemon.menu
 Append S:ToolsDaemonMenus/Toolsdaemon.Mame S:ToolsDaemon.menu
 Assign ScummVM: Emulators2:ScummVM
 Assign Mame: Emulators2:Mame
Endif

If $DEVMODE EQ 1
 Append S:ToolsDaemonMenus/Toolsdaemon.DevMode S:ToolsDaemon.menu
Endif

Append S:ToolsDaemonMenus/Toolsdaemon.End S:ToolsDaemon.menu

Search >NIL: T:Drives AGS_Drive QUIET
If not warn
 Execute S:AGS-Stuff
Endif